    <title>Tangential varieties of Segre-Veronese varieties</title>
    <summary>  We determine the minimal generators of the ideal of the tangential variety of
a Segre-Veronese variety, as well as the decomposition into irreducible
GL-representations of its homogeneous coordinate ring. In the special case of a
Segre variety, our results confirm a conjecture of Landsberg and Weyman.
</summary>
